These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, daisy, zinnia, rose
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, rugby, handball, basketball
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, superhero, satire, fantasy
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, british, nigerian, pakistani
1. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the british##1
3. the person watching satire movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
6. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
7. the person who's sport is rugby is the colombian##1
8. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the nigerian##1
9. the person who growsrose is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Flower         | daffodil  | rose  | daisy | zinnia |
| Sport           | rugby | baseball | basketball  | handball  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy       | satire      | family | superhero      |
| Nationality           | colombian          | british     | nigerian    | pakistani     |

