.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, turquise, blood-red, amber
City: colone, rome, boston, berlin
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, november, february, october
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, western, epic, scientific
1. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person who likes blood-red is the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
8. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
9. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Color      | blood-red     | pink       | turquise | amber        |
| City          | berlin     | rome       | boston   | colone   |
| Birthday   | february      | november       | october     | april    |
| Movie-Genre         | epic | scientific | time-travel | western |

