.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, nigerian, italian, egyptian
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, tram, bike, van
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, november, october, july
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, lilac, amber, coral
 1. the egyptian is the person who likes coral##1
 2. the italian is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
 4. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 5. the german is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 8. the italian is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 9. the german is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
10. the italian is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Nationality      | nigerian | german       | egyptian        | italian        |
| Transport           | tram   | bike | airplane   | van |
| Birthday   | february     | november    | july | october        |
| Color           | amber         | brown  | coral       | lilac         |

