3. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
5. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
8. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
9. the person who likes chestnut is the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Birthday           | february   | march  | january | august |
| City   | prague | liverpool       | new-york       | miami     |
