.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, alhambra, bongani, old-henry
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, juice, almond-milk
City: rome, colone, new-york, boston
There 4 different types of food: onion, zucchini, eggplant, cherry
1. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
2. the person eating onion is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
3. the person eating zucchini is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
6. the person eating cherry is the person traveling to new-york##1
7. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
9. the person drinking cola is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Cigar           | swisher  | bongani    | alhambra | old-henry |
| Beverage   | juice      | hot-chocolate    | cola         | almond-milk    |
| City   | colone   | rome     | new-york          | boston      |
| Food         | zucchini | onion | cherry      | eggplant      |

