 7. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the chaman-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| City          | hannover  | rome | edinburgh     | paris |
| Cigar           | chaman  | vegafina      | siglo | davidoff    |
