 4. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the person playing whist is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the prince-smoker is the colombian##1
 8. the person who likes red is on the far left##1
 9. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
10. the nigerian is on the left of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Color    | red | lilac     | fuchsia    | azure |
| Game       | bridge | backgammon    | monopoly | whist |
| Cigar         | havana   | chaman  | old-henry        | prince    |
