4. the cottage house is the person eating zucchini##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the nurse##1
7. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person eating pear##1
8. the person eating raspberry is the ranch-style house##1
9. the person watching family movies is on the right of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
