 5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 6. the person who growsiris is on the right of the colombian##1
 7. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 8. the russian is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the canadian is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the owner of the frog is the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3       |     4     |
| Pet          | chinchilla  | fish   | frog       | lizard     |
