 3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the analyst##1
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is the scientist##1
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the cottage house##1
 8. the scientist is the person playing bridge##1
 9. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4     |
| Hobby      | baking | sudoku     | rock-climbing          | singing |
| House   | farmhouse   | cottage       | art-deco     | craftsman   |
| Job   | scientist    | dancer  | analyst         | software-developer     |
| Game         | bridge | mah-jongg | monopoly | whist  |

 